# Admin access for the Model Registry:
#  - Preferred: sign in via /login with a Supabase Auth user that has
#    app_metadata.role = "admin". The dashboard sends the JWT to the
#    model-register and model-deactivate Edge Functions.
#  - Backstop only (private/internal builds): set the shared admin token
#    below. Must match the MODEL_REGISTRY_ADMIN_TOKEN secret on the Edge
#    Functions. Never configure on public static hosting.
# VITE_MODEL_REGISTRY_ADMIN_TOKEN=
